<i>noun</i>: 역 [역], 상극 [상극], 반면 [반ː면], 반대 [반ː대] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>역 [역]</dt><br>
<dd>opposite; converse; reverse</dd><br>
<dd>반대 또는 거꾸로인 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that is the opposite or the other way around.</dd><br>
<dt>상극 [상극]</dt><br>
<dd>1. opposite; disaccord; incompatibility</dd><br>
<dd>서로 마음이 맞지 않아 맞서거나 부딪침.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of clashing with each other because two groups are in conflict.</dd><br>
<dd>2. incompatibility; opposite</dd><br>
<dd>서로 맞서거나 해가 되어 어울릴 수 없는 상태나 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or quality of standing against each other, being unable to get along well.</dd><br>
<dt>반면 [반ː면]</dt><br>
<dd>opposite; contrast; other side</dd><br>
<dd>뒤에 오는 말이 앞의 내용과는 반대임.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the meaning of following words are opposite to that of preceding words.</dd><br>
<dt>반대 [반ː대]</dt><br>
<dd>1. opposite; contrary</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 다른 것과 모양, 위치, 방향, 속성 등에서 완전히 다름.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which something is completely different from another thing in its shape, position, direction, quality, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. opposition; objection</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 행동이나 의견 등을 따르지 않고 거스름.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being against a certain behavior, opinion, etc., without following it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>